title: Your Mediacal Record Are Save
description: This warning label should appear on every patient health record, with each test or procedure we have, and with each office visit. We sign a mandatory form protecting the privacy of our health information, but we aren't provided a similar form that assures the availability of our medical records to the one person who needs them the most—you.
